Clone the repo and follow the tutorial.
What you need to do
[ ] Clone the repo
[ ] Add a nav and footer using {% include %}
[ ] Create a content area using {% block content %}
[ ] Make pages extend the base template using {% extends %}
[ ] Wire up the index route in app.py
[ ] Add a new route for the market update page
[ ] Build out the “Latest news & updates” section
[ ] Create a reusable card macro
[ ] Add styling to match the design